      public void solicitud_longitudes_m(double equivalente, String nombre)
      The function "solicitud_longitudes_m" takes in an equivalent value and a name, prompts the user to enter a length, performs a conversion, and displays the converted length.
      Parameters:
      equivalente - The parameter "equivalente" is a double value that represents the conversion factor from the inputted length to the desired length unit. It is used to calculate the converted length.
      nombre - The parameter "nombre" is a String that represents the unit of measurement for the converted length.
